'''Mochudi Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Gaborone]], [[Botswana]].  It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as the home stadium of [[Centre Chiefs]].  The stadium holds 10,000 people.  

