Prokopova participated at the [[2012 Summer Olympics]] in London.<ref>{{cite web|author=Watch the film |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/olympics/2012/athletes/1e78a296-cb65-4a6f-9d6a-114b8a2b4891 |title=BBC Sport - London 2012 Olympics - Svitlana Prokopova : Ukraine, Gymnastics - Rhythmic |website=Bbc.com |date=2012-08-13 |accessdate=2017-03-07}}</ref> She competed at world championships, including at the 2011 and at the [[2013 World Rhythmic Gymnastics Championships]],<ref>{{cite web|title=2013 World Rhythmic Gymnastics Championships athletes - Svitlana Prokopova|url=http://gym.longinestiming.com/File/00000C0101FFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF02|publisher=Longinestiming.com|date= |accessdate=27 January 2016}}</ref> winning the silver medal in the bronze in the 10 clubs event.
