{{unreferenced|date=February 2010}}{{Notability|sport|date=July 2013}}
The '''Walsh Cup''' has been competed for since 1967 by the [[Navy Midshipmen#Men's crew|U.S. Naval Academy]] and [[Wisconsin Badgers Crew#Cups and trophies|Wisconsin]] Men's Varsity Eight [[College rowing (United States)|rowing]] teams. Both teams compete in the [[Eastern Association of Rowing Colleges]] (EACR).

It is named after Commander [[Charles "Buck" Walsh]], former coach of the U.S. Naval Academy crew.

