'''Youssouf Hiss Bachir''' (born 1 January 1987) is a Djiboutian [[Middle-distance running|middle-distance runner]].<ref name="Bio">{{cite web |url=http://www.iaaf.org/athletes/djibouti/youssouf-hiss-bachir-259496 |title=Youssouf Hiss Bachir |accessdate=13 March 2014 |work=IAAF}}</ref> He represented his country at two indoor and one outdoor World Championships.
